Budman here.

00:39.205 --> 00:40.623
Hey, what's up?

00:40.707 --> 00:43.293
Oh, man, I never realized

00:43.376 --> 00:44.627
{\an3}they managed
all these artists.

00:44.711 --> 00:46.129
{\an1}Who do you think
they're going

00:46.212 --> 00:47.589
{\an1}to give us for
our first video?

00:47.672 --> 00:48.631
{\an3}Who cares?

00:48.715 --> 00:51.092
{\an3}This is like
the Hall of Fame.

00:51.176 --> 00:52.302
Look at this.

00:52.385 --> 00:53.970
{\an6}BUDMAN:
Are we go for
this weekend?

00:55.930 --> 00:59.309
Great. Thanks, buddy.

00:59.392 --> 01:02.145
{\an3}I knew this was
going to be magic.

01:02.228 --> 01:03.813
We just signed
this amazing band.

01:03.897 --> 01:04.980
You're doing their video.

01:05.063 --> 01:07.317
{\an3}I've been trying for weeks
to set up a showcase for them,

01:07.400 --> 01:08.651
and the minute we lock you,

01:08.735 --> 01:10.737
the club calls with an open date
this weekend.

01:10.820 --> 01:13.448
{\an3}(laughs)
That's great.

01:13.531 --> 01:14.824
Saturday night
at the Peach Pit After Dark.

01:14.908 --> 01:15.825
It's on Olympic.

01:15.909 --> 01:16.743
Yeah, we know it.

01:16.826 --> 01:18.536
{\an3}Actually we, we kind of
know the owner.

01:18.620 --> 01:19.996
See? It's karma.

01:20.079 --> 01:21.998
Who's the group?

01:22.081 --> 01:23.291
{\an3}Nobody yet.

01:23.374 --> 01:24.501
But they are so hot.

01:24.584 --> 01:25.460
Especially the singer.

01:25.543 --> 01:28.838
{\an3}Plays great guitar,
writes all the material.

01:28.922 --> 01:30.131
Drop-dead sexy, this guy.

01:30.215 --> 01:31.174
They're gonna be huge.

01:31.257 --> 01:33.968
Guy's name is Pruit.
Ray Pruit.

