{\an3}Hold on, tell me this
isn't <i> Matt Houston?</i>

10:11.110 --> 10:12.653
Oh, this is my favorite show.

10:12.737 --> 10:14.030
{\an1}I watched it all the time
as a kid.

10:14.113 --> 10:15.990
{\an3}I've seen
every episode.

10:16.073 --> 10:17.199
