to school by helicopter.

10:19.618 --> 10:20.536
Well, join us, brother.

10:20.620 --> 10:22.246
You're in good company.

10:22.330 --> 10:23.789
Oh, this is the one
where the gourmet chef

10:23.873 --> 10:26.542
{\an1}is found murdered
in the bowl of Jell-O.

10:26.625 --> 10:28.544
Clare, come here.
You have to see this.

10:28.627 --> 10:29.879
No, I don't.

10:29.962 --> 10:31.881
What's the matter with her?

10:31.964 --> 10:33.716
Hmm, she's bored.

10:33.799 --> 10:34.884
{\an1}Look,?

10:34.967 --> 10:36.385
you want to make
me feel better?

10:36.469 --> 10:37.720
{\an3}(chuckles)

10:37.803 --> 10:39.555
Get her out of here.

10:39.639 --> 10:41.724
Clare, why don't you
get dressed?

10:41.807 --> 10:42.725
I'm taking you

10:42.808 --> 10:45.227
{\an3}to dinner--
anywhere you want.

10:45.311 --> 10:48.022
Good, as long
as it's not with him.

10:48.105 --> 10:49.231
(growls)

10:49.315 --> 10:50.691
Don't worry, Steve.
She's in good hands.

10:50.775 --> 10:52.693
I'll bring her home
in one piece.

10:52.777 --> 10:55.529
{\an3}Hey, um, do you want something
to drink while you wait?

10:55.613 --> 10:57.239
No, sit down.

10:57.323 --> 10:59.408
{\an3}Just point me in
the right direction.

10:59.492 --> 11:01.827
Good.o-over there.

11:03.287 --> 11:07.249
{\an1}Well, Carl sure jumped at
the chance to take out Clare.

11:07.333 --> 11:08.459
Ah, they're
old friends.

11:08.542 --> 11:10.961
Okay, just checking.

11:13.297 --> 11:15.299
Relax.

11:20.346 --> 11:21.931
You shouldn't
have run, man.

11:22.014 --> 11:24.600
The rest of us all got
off on illegal search.

11:24.683 --> 11:25.684
They dropped the charges

11:25.768 --> 11:28.479
{\an5}while you were doing
your,
uh, O.J. imitation.

11:28.562 --> 11:29.647
(laughs)

11:32.149 --> 11:33.567
It's pretty funny, actually.

11:33.651 --> 11:34.777
Yeah, that's hilarious,
isn't it?

11:34.860 --> 11:35.820
I don't know.

11:35.903 --> 11:37.405
Maybe you should
just do the deuce.

11:37.488 --> 11:38.572
Get it over with.

11:38.656 --> 11:39.824
What are you, nuts?

11:39.907 --> 11:41.867
It ain't happening, man.

11:41.951 --> 11:42.993
{\an3}Your call.

11:44.161 --> 11:46.080
So, uh, what's your plan?

11:46.163 --> 11:47.998
My plan is to get out
of this country.

11:48.082 --> 11:51.085
{\an3}My plan is to hit the border
as fast as I Wow.

11:51.168 --> 11:52.294
