because of you.

12:07.059 --> 12:08.519
Now you want to rip me off?

12:08.602 --> 12:09.979
Hey, hey, hey!

12:10.062 --> 12:12.189
I'm sorry about what
went down, all right?

12:12.273 --> 12:14.066
But the scratch ain't for me.

12:14.150 --> 12:15.359
It's for the paper.

12:16.402 --> 12:18.821
(whispers):
I'm sorry.

12:18.904 --> 12:21.323
{\an1}This whole thing
has me all wound up.

12:21.407 --> 12:22.867
All right, no worries.

12:28.414 --> 12:31.250
All right, I'll do
my best, all right?

12:32.251 --> 12:33.669
{\an3}Here.

12:33.752 --> 12:35.379
{\an3}Take this.

12:35.463 --> 12:37.673
{\an3}I just fired one
of my delivery boys.

12:37.756 --> 12:40.092
{\an3}I'll beep you
when I got what you need.

12:48.601 --> 12:50.186
{\an1}Thank you.

12:50.269 --> 12:51.645
Thank you.

12:51.729 --> 12:54.690
{\an1}I take it Steve's
I love him,iest patient.

12:54.774 --> 12:55.858
but, um, if you hadn't

12:55.941 --> 12:57.234
have gotten me out
of there tonight,

12:57.318 --> 12:59.695
{\an3}you may have found him dead
in t(chuckling)

12:59.778 --> 13:01.363
Well, to be honest,
if Steve hadn't suggested

13:01.447 --> 13:03.699
I take you to dinner,
I would have done it anyway.

13:03.782 --> 13:05.493
{\an3}You can't wait on him
hand and foot.

13:05.576 --> 13:06.869
Even a prince like Steve needs

13:06.952 --> 13:08.871
to fend for himself
every once in a while.

13:08.954 --> 13:10.873
And what about a prince
like you?

